<p><i><b>Orientalism</b></i> is the 1978 book by <a href="/wiki/Edward_Said" title="Edward Said">Edward Said</a> that has been highly influential in <a href="/wiki/Postcolonialism" title="Postcolonialism">postcolonial studies</a>.</p>
